gotDieCmd

public void gotDieCmd(java.lang.String recipient)
This method logs the bot off.

Parameters:
recipient - is the bot that is supposed to recieve the command. If it is null than all pubbots recieve it and thus a chat message is not necessary.

gotWhereCmd

public void gotWhereCmd()
This method handles the where command from the pubhubbot. It waits for the arena info to be updated and then sends the current arena back to the pubhubbot.

gotGoCmd

public void gotGoCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method makes the bot change arenas.

Parameters:
argString - is the new arena to go to.

gotLoadCmd

public void gotLoadCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method checks to see if loading a module is possible (ie the module is present). If it is, it sends an "loading" message to the pubhub bot.

Parameters:
argString - is the name of the module to load.

gotUnloadCmd

public void gotUnloadCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method checks to see if unloading a module is possible (ie the module is present). If it is, it sends an "unloading" message to the pubhub bot.

Parameters:
argString - is the name of the module to unload.

gotLoadedCmd

public void gotLoadedCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method loads and initializes a module from the bot. It is called when the pubhub bot sends the loaded message via IPC.

Parameters:
argString - is the module to load.

gotUnloadedCmd

public void gotUnloadedCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method unloads a module from the bot. It is called when the pubhub bot sends the unloaded message via IPC.

Parameters:
argString - is the module to unload.

gotJoinChatCmd

public void gotJoinChatCmd(java.lang.String argString)
This method handles the join chat command from the pubhubbot.

Parameters:
argString - is the chat to join.

handlePlayerIPC

                            java.lang.String sender,
                            java.lang.String message)

Parameters:
botSender - is the bot that issued the IPC command.
